field.name: MSG_PREPARE_AD_LOADING
field.value: "An ad is currently loading. Please wait for the ad to finish loading and showing before loading another ad."

field.name: MSG_PREPARE_AD_READY_TO_SHOW
field.value: "An ad is ready to show. Please call showAd() to show the ad before loading another ad."

field.name: MSG_PREPARE_AD_SHOWING
field.value: "An ad is currently showing. Please wait for the user to dismiss the ad before loading an ad."

field.name: MSG_SHOW_AD_ANOTHER_SHOWING
field.value: "Another ad is currently showing. Please wait for the AdListener.onAdDismissed callback of the other ad."

field.name: MSG_SHOW_AD_DESTROYED
field.value: "The ad cannot be shown because it has been destroyed. Create a new Ad object to load a new ad."

field.name: MSG_SHOW_AD_DISMISSED
field.value: "The ad cannot be shown because it has already been displayed to the user. Please call loadAd(AdTargetingOptions) to load a new ad."

field.name: MSG_SHOW_AD_EXPIRED
field.value: "This ad has expired. Please load another ad."

field.name: MSG_SHOW_AD_LOADING
field.value: "The ad cannot be shown because it is still loading. Please wait for the AdListener.onAdLoaded() callback before showing the ad."

field.name: MSG_SHOW_AD_READY_TO_LOAD
field.value: "The ad cannot be shown because it has not loaded successfully. Please call loadAd(AdTargetingOptions) to load an ad first."

field.name: MSG_SHOW_AD_SHOWING
field.value: "The ad cannot be shown because it is already displayed on the screen. Please wait for the AdListener.onAdDismissed() callback and then load a new ad."
